title: Start
body:
Jaycee: Hi! Are you a pledge too?

[[Yes!|101]]
[[Mhm.|101]]

EP: It's so nice to meet you!! My name is EP.

[[My name is Lucy.|201]]
[[Mine is Lucy!|201]]

EP: This is so exciting!! You like have to meet, um... I'm, um, so sorry, what's your name again?
CP: My name is CP.
EP: Ohh no, that's right. I totally forgot, I'm sorry, I'm so bad with names!
CP: It's okay! No worries.

[[Nice to meet you!|301]]
[[This is so exciting!|302]]

CP: I know! I can't believe this is finally happening.
EP: What did you guys think of the speech and everything?

[[It was great!|401]]
[[She seems so cool.|402]]

CP: Yea, it's nice to meet you too!
EP: What did you guys think of the speech and everything?

[[It was great!|401]]
[[She seems so cool.|402]]

Jaycee: Oh my god, so cool. The commandments and everything were like so cute.
Kayla: I don't know, a couple of them were kind of weird.
Jaycee: What do you mean?? Like, which ones?
Kayla: Uhhh... I mean, the one about puking in public was kinda weird, 'cause like, sometimes you don't really have a choice, you know?
Jaycee: What? And embarrass our family? Are you kidding?

[[It's just weird because you're new.|501]]
[[Yea, it was a little weird.|502]]

Jaycee: Oh my god, so great. The commandments and everything were like so cute.
Kayla: I don't know, a couple of them were kind of weird.
Jaycee: What do you mean?? Like, which ones?
Kayla: Uhhh... I mean, the one about puking in public was kinda weird, 'cause like, sometimes you don't really have a choice, you know?
Jaycee: What? And embarrass our family? Are you kidding?

[[It's just weird because you're new.|501]]
[[Yea, it was a little weird.|502]]

Jaycee: What?? I can't believe you guys are saying this.
Kayla: Yea, I don't know.
Jaycee: I think we should be really grateful for them letting us stay here and everything. 
Jaycee: They're doing a really nice thing for us, and they're like so welcoming.
Jaycee: I mean like the least we can do is follow their rules, you know?
Kayla: I just feel weird about having to follow rules just to be friends with people.

[[I know what you mean.|601]]
[[I think it'll pass.|602]]

Jaycee: Yea, it's just because you're new.
Kayla: I don't know, I guess.
Jaycee: I mean, I think we should be really grateful for them letting us stay here and everything. 
Jaycee: It takes a lot of time and effort and like, money for this sort of thing, you know?
Jaycee: We can totally like follow their rules in return, you know?
Kayla: I just feel weird about having to follow rules just to be friends with people.

[[I know what you mean.|601]]
[[The feeling will pass.|602]]

Kayla: Yea, you're probably right.
Kayla: I mean, I'm not trying to say I hate them or anything, or like, I'm going to leave.
Kayla: I get anxious about things sometimes, I'm... probably overthinking it.
Jaycee: Well that's what they're here for, you know?
Jaycee: Like, your anxiety. They're your sisters now, and they're here to support you.
Kayla: Yea, that's true.

[[It's going to be okay.|701]]
[[We're here for you.|702]]

Jaycee: I'm just so surprised.
Kayla: I mean I'm not trying to say I hate them or anything, or like, I'm going to leave.
Kayla: I get anxious about things sometimes, I'm probably overthinking it.
Jaycee: Well that's what they're here for, you know?
Jaycee: Like, your anxiety. They're your sisters now, and they're here to support you.
Kayla: Yea, that's true.

[[It's going to be okay.|701]]
[[We're here for you.|702]]

Jaycee: Yea, we're totally here for you.
Kayla: Thanks, you guys, I really appreciate it.
Kayla: I'm really sorry for being so weird, I wasn't trying to be too negative or anything.

[[It's okay!|801]]
[[No worries.|801]]

Jaycee: Yea, it's totally going to be okay.
Kayla: Thanks, you guys, I really appreciate it.
Kayla: I'm really sorry for being so weird, I wasn't trying to be too negative or anything.

[[It's okay!|801]]
[[No worries.|801]]

Kayla smiles.

[[I'm gonna go, I'll talk to you guys soon.|901]]
[[I'm gonna go meet some more pledges!|901]]

Kayla: Okay! Have fun.
Jaycee: See you soon!!
